# Backend

- Models and migrations: `backend/prisma/`; HTTP handlers in `backend/src/routes/*` (wired in `backend/src/app.ts`).
- When serializing amounts and currencies, follow patterns in `routeSupport.ts` and domain modules (`toNumber`, `normalizeCurrency`).
- FX rates: `backend/src/fx.ts` — do not duplicate FX logic in route handlers.
- REST endpoints under `/api/...`; JSON responses; appropriate HTTP status codes on errors.
- Secrets only in `.env` (do not commit); `dotenv` loads configuration at startup.
- Endpoint catalog: [docs/api.md](mdc:docs/api.md) — add one table row when adding routes.
- Tests: [docs/testing.md](mdc:docs/testing.md).
